What we didn't like was how it was packaged, since everything comes in a very tight box, and some accessories are deformed and some broken, I suppose due to the pressure of everything being put in the box (the mannequin was a gift for my niece, and, of course, she started playing with it, if she hadn't asked for a replacement because of the accessories). review_body: Es el tercero que compro, ninguno de los 3 ha marcado bien la temperatura real de la estancia. 2 estaban un par de grados por debajo y el tercero un par de grados por encima. Por lo demás funcionan bien, calientan muy rápidos y valen la pena calidad precio.
translated_review: It is the third one I have bought, none of the 3 have correctly marked the real temperature of the room. 2 were a couple of degrees below and the third a couple of degrees above. The solution is to put reliable thermometers nearby, find out the margin of error and from there program it so that they maintain the real temperature you want. Otherwise they work well, heat up very quickly and are worth the price.

Anda bastante lento un par de km hora podían haberle dado y alguna palanca para el cambio de marcha en vez de botón. Y aunque sea de mentira cualquier cosa más ya que más simplón no puede ser. Aunque sea el más barato no lo volvería a comprar. Ni un triste claxon...
translated_review: The car is quite simple. We bought it because it was one of the cheapest for Santa Claus and well...the assembly was not very specified, especially the stickers. It is simple but functional. He doesn't carry anything. Only front lights that you can barely see the brake, accelerator and steering wheel. March forward and backward. With a very hard button for 3-year-old children. The car is made of plastic but of poor quality and it came with factory imperfections that we were able to solve ourselves. Quite uncomfortable when the child is driving the position. It runs quite slowly, a couple of km per hour could have been given and some gear change lever instead of a button. And even if anything else is a lie, it couldn't be simpler. Even if it is the cheapest I would not buy it again. Not a sad horn...

review_body: No soporta bien la interperie, y eso que vivo en un lugar donde no llueve mucho. Al principio no alumbraba mal pero dura poco.

At first it didn't shine badly but it didn't last long.

review_body: Lo mejor de la tablet es la rapidez de la carga y la capacidad de memoria. Lo peor el sonido se oye muy poco, aunque no lo he probado con auriculares, la calidad del mismo es bastante inferior a otras tablets de su rango. También he notado que en la navegación de internet funciona muy lento al escribir el texto en el buscador. Por lo demás, tiene buena imagen en HD y la duración de la carga de la batería también es aceptable, me he visto una retransmisión deportiva de 2 horas y al finalizar la misma aún disponía del 45% de carga, lo que supongo que dará para ver video durante otras 2 horas
translated_review: The best thing about the tablet is the speed of loading and the memory capacity. The worst thing is that you can hear very little sound, although I have not tried it with headphones, its quality is much lower than other tablets in its range. I have also noticed that when browsing the Internet it works very slowly when writing text in the search engine. For the rest, it has a good HD image and the battery charge duration is also acceptable, I watched a 2-hour sports broadcast and at the end of it I still had 45% charge, which I suppose will last for watch video for another 2 hours

Además una cosa que me gusta que tiene "un clip", que te lo enganchas al cuello de una camisa, etc y puedes escucharla sin cascos.
translated_review: At the time I had a mini digital radio that lasted a long time. This Elbe works a little differently and it's hard for me to get used to it (because I had the previous one for a long time). But I am very happy with it. Plus the rechargeable batteries I put in last a long time. Also, one thing I like is that it has "a clip", that you can clip it to the collar of a shirt, etc. and you can listen to it without headphones.

review_body: He tenido varios auriculares de esta gama de precios y me compré éstos dejándome llevar por las buenas opiniones de otros compradores. Bueno, pues me han decepcionado completamente, por la calidad de sus materiales y sobre todo por la calidad de sonido, muy inferior a la de otros de un mismo precio, o incluso inferior... he tenido un par de ellos de la marca TaoTronics que ofrecían mucha más calidad. En estos los bajos apenas se aprecian, el sonido es muy metálico y agudo, como a lata... lo propio de auriculares baratos, pero que al final salen caros. Si no eres muy riguroso con esa calidad de sonido estos auriculares pueden servirte, pero a nada que desees una cierta calidad, mejor buscar otros...

Well, they have completely disappointed me, due to the quality of their materials and especially the sound quality, much lower than that of others of the same price, or even lower... I have had a pair of them from the TaoTronics brand that offered much higher quality. In these the bass is barely noticeable, the sound is very metallic and sharp, like a tin can... typical of cheap headphones, but in the end they are expensive. If you are not very strict with that sound quality, these headphones can help you, but unless you want a certain quality, it is better to look for others...

review_body: Hace unos días realicé un pedido por amazon de un pack 2 pistones para bisagra de canape de 135. Después de Mas de una semana de espera por el producto (tengo amazon prime), he recibido el paquete roto y con sólo uno de los pistones. Me gustaría saber que puedo hacer para recibir el pistón que falta. Creo que no se ha cumplido ni con el plazo de entrega ni con le mercancía y por lo tanto creo que merezco una compensación por ello. Por lo menos recibir el producto completo. Quedó a la espera de su respuesta. Gracias.
translated_review: A few days ago I placed an order through Amazon for a pack of 2 pistons for a 135 canape hinge. After more than a week of waiting for the product (I have Amazon Prime), I received the package broken and with only one of the pistons. I would like to know what I can do to receive the missing piston. I believe that neither the delivery time nor the merchandise has been met and therefore I believe that I deserve compensation for it. At least receive the complete product. I await your response. Thank you.

review_body: Buen protector, totalmente transparente, cristal de calidad seguro. Trasmite buena sensación una vez puesto y no entorpece para nada la experiencia con la pantalla. Probado en samsung s10 la unica pega en mi opinion: no llega a los bordes. Aun con una funda que protega, el gap sigue siendo demasiaso grande a mi gusto. No interfiere para nada en el acceso al edge panel. Recomiendo, aunque debo decir seguiré buscando uno que cubra mas los bordes. Ya veremos que tal soporta los golpes

It slides perfectly and keeps its transparency under the sun. The easy installation kit is greatly appreciated. It also comes with 3 units with everything necessary for 3 installations. Tested on Samsung S10, the only drawback in my opinion: it doesn't reach the edges. Even with a protective case, the gap is still too big for my liking. It does not interfere at all with access to the edge panel. I recommend, although I must say I will continue looking for one that covers the edges more. We'll see how it withstands the blows.

Respecto a la relación calidad precio, no tengo muchas cosas buenas que decir; se trata de cuatro palos y un trozo de tela.

The ropes that tie the poles begin to unravel until they no longer secure them and the tipi is dismantled. I've had it tucked away in a corner for several days now. review_body: El producto es tal cual el que te ofrecen. Solo tengo dos pegas; la primera es que el receptor no se apaga cuando apagas el pc, por lo que te toca instalar un programa que de encargue de ello para que no esté la luz encendida continuamente, y la segunda es que si tienes la mala suerte de que el CD de drivers no funcione o no tengas lector de CD en tu torre te toca buscarlos manualmente (trabajo el cual se me ha hecho complicado ya que hay que engañar a Windows 10 para que lo detecte como un dispositivo original). Por lo demás es un buen producto cumpliendo con lo que promete, una buena sincronización (aunque la primera vez cuesta un poco) y alcance más que óptimo para jugar desde la otra punta de la habitación si te apetece.
translated_review: The product is just like the one they offer you. I only have two problems; The first is that the receiver does not turn off when you turn off the PC, so you have to install a program to take care of this so that the light is not on continuously, and the second is that if you are unlucky enough that the CD driver does not work or you do not have a CD reader in your tower, you have to search for them manually (a job which has been complicated for me since you have to trick Windows 10 into detecting it as an original device). For the rest, it is a good product that does what it promises, good synchronization (although it costs a little the first time) and more than optimal range to play from the other side of the room if you feel like it.

review_body: Hasta la fecha, siempre he pelado mis perros con tijera, laborioso pero al menos no se asustaban, ya que no tengo bastantes ingresos para pagar un sitio oficial. No obstante, estaba determinada a probar una máquina, y después de leer todos los comentarios de las diversas maracas disponibles me quedé con éste, y de momento estoy encantada. Mi perro ni se inmuta - ni miedo ni nada, se queda tan tranquilito, y le he podido pelar tanto tiempo que quería sin ningún problema. El motivo de da solo 4 estrellas es que, aunque se enciende la lucecita roja al cargar y cuando se utiliza, no se apaga cuando la carga está completa, así que es difícil calcular la duración - suelo comprobar el enchufe, y cuando está frío, estará cargado. De todas maneras, nunca me ha dejado a medias, ha habido batería de sobra. Otra cosa que quizás faltaría sería la botellita de aceite, pero dado el precio, francamente no se puede pedir más. La máquina no se calienta como algunas, y es muy cómoda en la mano. En total, súper satisfecha - veremos cuánto dura !!!
translated_review: To date, I have always peeled my dogs with scissors, laborious but at least they were not scared, since I do not have enough income to pay for an official site. However, I was determined to try a machine, and after reading all the reviews of the various maracas available I settled on this one, and so far I am delighted. My dog ​​doesn't even flinch - not afraid or anything, he stays so calm, and I have been able to peel him for as long as he wanted without any problem. The reason it only gives 4 stars is that, although the little red light comes on when charging and when in use, it does not turn off when charging is complete, so it is difficult to estimate the duration - I usually check the plug, and when it is cold, will be loaded. In any case, it has never left me halfway, there has been plenty of battery. Another thing that might be missing would be the little bottle of oil, but given the price, frankly you can't ask for more. The machine does not get hot like some, and is very comfortable in the hand. In total, super satisfied - we'll see how long it lasts!!!

translated_review: Well, it doesn't adapt well to the mobile screen. There are areas where it sticks well and others where it is loose.

review_body: Adecuado para el precio; un pelin inestable pero bien!
translated_review: Adequate for the price; a bit unstable but good!

review_body: De los 4 comprados 1 de ellos no funciona y lo he devuelto para que me lo reembolsen o me envíen uno que sí que funcione. Los que funcionan tienen buena potencia de luz y color blanco frío, la pena es que no puedan dejarse enchufados , sino que sólo se enchufan cuando detectan movimiento.
translated_review: Of the 4 purchased, 1 of them does not work and I have returned it for a refund or to send me one that does work. The ones that work have good light output and a cool white color, the shame is that they cannot be left plugged in, but rather they only plug in when they detect movement.

review_body: Creía que era un cristal templado,pero es una pegatina,si cumple su función para evitar rayaduras pero ya encontré un cristal templado y la cambie
translated_review: I thought it was a tempered glass, but it is a sticker, it does fulfill its function to prevent scratches but I already found a tempered glass and changed it

review_body: muy mal me falto una pieza y me toco comprar algo parecido para poderlo armar lo pensare dos veces para volver a comprar productos por amazon ya que no me dieron ninguna solucion.
translated_review: Very bad, I was missing a piece and I had to buy something similar to be able to assemble it. I will think twice about buying products from Amazon again since they did not give me any solution.

review_body: Las baterias, estan bien pero son anchas, si tienes un syma x5 aunque lo pone, porque no te van a entrar asi q ten CUIDADO. Por lo demas bien. Traen un cable de adaptador para cargarlas.
translated_review: The batteries are good but they are wide, if you have a syma x5 even if it says so, because they are not going to fit so be CAREFUL. Otherwise well. They come with an adapter cable to charge them.

review_body: El listón estaba muy alto con la película original, y creo que pasa decentemente la prueba. Posiblemente algo más larga de lo que debiera, pero la película esta bien y para mí, como siempre, el 3D es un plus.
translated_review: The bar was set very high with the original film, and I think it passes the test decently. Possibly a little longer than it should be, but the film is good and for me, as always, the 3D is a plus.

review_body: En un mes ha dejado de funcionar
translated_review: In a month it stopped working

review_body: Lo he devuelto por qué la calidad del sonido pésima, además de que no se puede elegir álbum en modo USB. Una pena que una marca como ésta haga productos como éste que no están a la altura.
translated_review: I have returned it because the sound quality is terrible, plus you cannot choose an album in USB mode. It's a shame that a brand like this makes products like this that aren't up to par.

review_body: Perfecto. Muy buena calidad.
translated_review: Perfect. Very good quality.

review_body: Es fantástico...muy completo
translated_review: It's fantastic...very complete

review_body: Muy estable, rígido, con lineas sencillas pero elegantes...estamos muy contentos. al principio no me gustaba la idea pero ahora estoy muy contenta con su funcionalidad.
translated_review: Very stable, rigid, with simple but elegant lines...we are very happy. At first I didn't like the idea but now I am very happy with its functionality.

review_body: Al principio de comprar el iphone todo muy bien, pero tras tener casi dos años el movil, me está dando problemas, fui a una apple store y me dicen que al comprarlo con amazon el primer año de garantía se hacen cargo ellos pero el segundo año tiene que ser la persona que me lo vendió de amazon. La persona que me lo ha vendido no se hace responsable me dice que vaya a apple, siendo que ya he ido. Estoy a unos dias que me venza mi garantía y no tengo ningun tipo de respuesta. Cuidado con lo que comprais!!
translated_review: At the beginning of buying the iPhone everything was very good, but after having the phone for almost two years, it is giving me problems, I went to an Apple store and they told me that when I buy it with Amazon, they will take care of the first year of warranty, but the second year It has to be the person who sold it to me from Amazon. The person who sold it to me is not responsible and tells me to go to Apple, even though I have already gone. I'm a few days away from my warranty expiring and I don't have any type of response. Be careful what you buy!!

review_body: Me han dado buen resultado, cortan bien después de usarlas bastante para el trabajo que las compre.
translated_review: They have given me good results, they cut well after using them a lot for the job I bought them for.

review_body: Cumplen su función, para el precio que tienen. La calidad es normalita. Lo que si me gusta mucho es la esponja que viene con ellos, la uso para aplicar la base de maquillaje. La bolsita es practica para guardarlos. Me gusta los mangos de madera, son bonitos.
translated_review: They do their job, for the price they have. The quality is normal. What I really like is the sponge that comes with them, I use it to apply makeup base. The bag is practical to store them. I like the wooden handles, they're pretty.

review_body: Pesa un montón, creo que más de los cuatro kilos que dice, lo cual es bastante bueno para partir troncos gorditos para hacer leña, pero el filo es un desastre, la tuve que afilar muchísimo cuando me llegó y varias veces más, y eso que le doy un uso esporádico. Menos mal que es barata, porque la cabeza no va a durar mucho a este paso. parece un metal blandito...
translated_review: It weighs a lot, I think more than the four kilos it says, which is quite good for splitting thick logs to make firewood, but the edge is a disaster, I had to sharpen it a lot when it arrived and several times more, and that I use it sporadically. Thank goodness it's cheap, because the head isn't going to last long at this rate. It looks like soft metal...

review_body: El producto ha llegado con golpes y defectuoso quiero el reembolso de mi pedido
translated_review: The product has arrived damaged and defective. I want a refund for my order.

review_body: Avisar antes de que es la lengua si no la importación
translated_review: Notify before that it is the language if not the import

review_body: El cepillo es bonito y cumple perfectamente con su cometido, pero por desgracia al poco tiempo el plástico del mango ha empezado a agrietarse. Finalmente se ha caído la parte metálica que sujeta los pelos, diría que a los 6 meses de uso.
translated_review: The brush is beautiful and does its job perfectly, but unfortunately after a short time the plastic on the handle began to crack. Finally the metal part that holds the hairs has fallen off, I would say after 6 months of use.

review_body: El buho es bonito pero no se mueve, lleva en la parte de abajo un hueco que le quitas un tapon y hay un plastico para ponerle detras de la cabeza. Supuesta mente eso vale como la veleta que al soplar aire la cabeza se mueve, pero no es asi.
translated_review: The owl is pretty but it doesn't move, it has a hole at the bottom that you remove a plug from and there is a piece of plastic to put behind its head. Supposedly this is like the weather vane that moves your head when you blow air, but it is not like that.

review_body: Fantástica funda, bonita, bien hecha
translated_review: Fantastic case, pretty, well made

review_body: No está mal pero esperaba q fuese más fuerte es un patín muy flojo
translated_review: It's not bad but I expected it to be stronger, it's a very loose skate

review_body: Mi hija la utiliza de luz auxiliar por la noche. Se la enciende, le parpadea un poco,despues se queda fijo y al rato se apaga. No sirve para jugar ,por suerte me costo bastante poco, sino hubiera sido un chasco
translated_review: My daughter uses it as an auxiliary light at night. She turns it on, it flashes a little, after that it stays on and then turns off after a while. It's not useful for playing, luckily it cost me quite little, otherwise it would have been a disappointment
